README.md
     1→# xxhash
     6→xxhash is a Go implementation of the 64-bit [xxHash] algorithm, XXH64. This is a
     7→high-quality hashing algorithm that is much faster than anything in the Go
     8→standard library.
     9→
    10→This package provides a straightforward API:
